{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "f8e9d2c0-5678-abcd-ef01-234567890123",
    "name": "NearProp - Franchisee & Subscription APIs",
    "description": "# NearProp Franchisee & Subscription APIs\n\nThis collection contains endpoints related to franchisee district management, franchise requests, district revenue tracking, and subscription management in the NearProp platform.\n\n## Franchisee Management\nEnables users to request franchisee privileges for specific districts and for admins to manage these requests and assignments.\n\n## District Management\nAllows management of districts including creation, updates, and assignment to franchisees.\n\n## Revenue Management\nFacilitates tracking and management of revenue generated from districts managed by franchisees.\n\n## Subscription Management\nEnables users to subscribe to various plans offered by the platform.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Franchise Request Management",
      "description": "Endpoints for users to submit franchise requests and for admins to manage them",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Submit Franchise Request",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{userToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "districtId",
                  "value": "1",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "businessName",
                  "value": "My Real Estate Business",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "businessAddress",
                  "value": "123 Main St, Business District",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "experienceYears",
                  "value": "5",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "documents",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": "/path/to/document.pdf"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/franchisee/requests",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "franchisee", "requests"]
            },
            "description": "Submit a request to become a franchisee for a specific district. The user must be authenticated and have the USER role.\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `districtId`: ID of the district for which the franchise is requested\n- `businessName`: Name of the user's real estate business\n- `businessAddress`: Address of the business\n- `experienceYears`: Years of experience in real estate\n- `documents`: Supporting documents (optional)\n\n**Required Auth:**\n- Bearer token with USER role"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Franchise Request by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{userToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/franchisee/requests/{{requestId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "franchisee", "requests", "{{requestId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Retrieve details of a specific franchise request by its ID.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `requestId`: ID of the franchise request\n\n**Required Auth:**\n- Bearer token with ADMIN, USER, or FRANCHISEE role"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Requests by Status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/franchisee/requests/status/PENDING?page=0&size=10&sortBy=createdAt&direction=DESC",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "franchisee", "requests", "status", "PENDING"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "0"
                },
                {
                  "key": "size",
                  "value": "10"
                },
                {
                  "key": "sortBy",
                  "value": "createdAt"
                },
                {
                  "key": "direction",
                  "value": "DESC"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Retrieve franchise requests filtered by status.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `status`: Status of the requests (PENDING, APPROVED, REJECTED)\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- `page`: Page number (zero-based, default: 0)\n- `size`: Number of items per page (default: 10)\n- `sortBy`: Field to sort by (default: createdAt)\n- `direction`: Sort direction (ASC or DESC, default: DESC)\n\n**Required Auth:**\n- Bearer token with ADMIN role"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Process Franchise Request",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"status\": \"APPROVED\",\n    \"comments\": \"Application approved after review of qualifications and documentation.\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/franchisee/requests/{{requestId}}/process",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "franchisee", "requests", "{{requestId}}", "process"]
            },
            "description": "Process (approve or reject) a franchise request.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `requestId`: ID of the franchise request\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `status`: New status for the request (APPROVED or REJECTED)\n- `comments`: Admin comments about the decision\n\n**Required Auth:**\n- Bearer token with ADMIN role"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Check if District is Assigned",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{userToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/franchisee/requests/is-district-assigned/{{districtId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "franchisee", "requests", "is-district-assigned", "{{districtId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Check if a specific district is already assigned to a franchisee.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `districtId`: ID of the district\n\n**Required Auth:**\n- Bearer token (any authenticated user)"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Request Statistics",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/franchisee/requests/statistics",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "franchisee", "requests", "statistics"]
            },
            "description": "Get statistics of franchise requests by status.\n\n**Required Auth:**\n- Bearer token with ADMIN role"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Cancel Franchise Request",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{userToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/franchisee/requests/{{requestId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "franchisee", "requests", "{{requestId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Cancel a franchise request. Only the user who submitted the request or a franchisee can cancel it.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `requestId`: ID of the franchise request\n\n**Required Auth:**\n- Bearer token with USER or FRANCHISEE role (must be the owner of the request)"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
